(16, 1, '2025-10-16 03:19:16', '2025-10-16 03:19:16', '<div class=\"ukroa-member-wrapper\">\r\n<h2 class=\"ukroa-member-title\">Choose your membership</h2>\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-slider\"><center><span class=\"ukroa-member-nav ukroa-member-prev\" aria-label=\"Previous\">❮</span></center>\r\n<center><span class=\"ukroa-member-nav ukroa-member-next\" aria-label=\"Next\">❯</span></center>\r\n<div id=\"ukroa-member-track\" class=\"ukroa-member-track\">\r\n\r\n<!-- Card 1 -->\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-card\">\r\n<h3>General Membership</h3>\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-price\">$30 <small>/triennial</small></div>\r\n<a href=\"../membership_form/?type=General+Membership&amp;amount=30\"><button class=\"ukroa-member-btn\">Join Now</button></a>\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-desc\">Membership shall be granted to any Kirat-Rai individual who can trace their ethnic origin to an indigenous Kirat-Rai ancestor of Nepal, as well as to non–Kirat-Rai individuals who wish to obtain membership through marriage and have adopted the Kirat-Rai surname, provided they abide by the mission of UKROA and remain members in good standing.\r\nThe membership fee is $30 for a three-year term for the general public, with a 50% discount available to student members.Students get <strong>50% discount</strong>. Valid for 3 years.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Card 2 -->\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-card\">\r\n<h3>Life Membership</h3>\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-price\">$200</div>\r\n<a href=\"../membership_form/?type=General+Membership&amp;amount=30\"><button class=\"ukroa-member-btn\">Join Now</button></a>\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-desc\">Membership shall be granted exclusively to Kirat-Rai individuals. The membership fee is $200 or more. Admission to membership shall be granted at the discretion of the Board upon thorough review and approval of the applicant’s application.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Card 3 -->\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-card\">\r\n<h3>Patron Membership</h3>\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-price\">$1001</div>\r\n<a href=\"../membership_form/?type=General+Membership&amp;amount=30\"><button class=\"ukroa-member-btn\">Join Now</button></a>\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-desc\">This membership shall be granted to any Kirat-Rai general member or past office bearer who possesses deep knowledge of the organization, has extensive work experience within UKROA, and is in good standing as a general member. The membership fee shall be $1001.00 or more. Membership approval is subject to the Board’s decision following a review of the applicant’s application. The patron member’s photograph shall be permanently displayed on the UKROA website unless the patron requests otherwise.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<!-- Card 4 -->\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-card\">\r\n<h3>Associate Membership</h3>\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-price\">$30 or $200</div>\r\n<a href=\"../membership_form/?type=General+Membership&amp;amount=30\"><button class=\"ukroa-member-btn\">Join Now</button></a>\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-desc\">This membership shall be granted to both Kirat-Rai and non–Kirat-Rai individuals. The Associate Membership fee shall be either $30 for a three-year term or a one-time payment of $200.00 or more. Associate Members are not eligible to serve as the Central Executive Committee President or as a Local Chapter Executive Committee President. This membership may be granted to individuals residing anywhere in the world.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<!-- Card 5 -->\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-card\">\r\n<h3>Honorary Membership</h3>\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-price\"> Free </div>\r\n<a href=\"../membership_form/?type=General+Membership&amp;amount=30\"><button class=\"ukroa-member-btn\">Join Now</button></a>\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-desc\">This membership shall be offered to individuals recognized as honorable at the national or international level, as well as to Presidents of organizations other than UKROA. No membership fee is required for this category.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Card 6 -->\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-card\">\r\n<h3>Institutional / Corporate</h3>\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-price\">$300 <small>/triennial</small></div>\r\n<a href=\"../membership_form/?type=General+Membership&amp;amount=30\"><button class=\"ukroa-member-btn\">Join Now</button></a>\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-member-desc\">For organizations supporting Kirat-Rai community.\r\nBenefits and full details coming soon.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Membership Application Modal + Payment -->\r\n<div id=\"ukroa-membership-modal\" class=\"ukroa-modal\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-modal-content\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"ukroa-close-btn\">×</span>\r\n<h2>Membership Application</h2>\r\n<div id=\"selected-plan\" style=\"background: #f0f8ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; font-size: 1.2em; color: #8b1e1e;\"></div>\r\n<form id=\"ukroa-membership-form\"><input id=\"membership_type\" name=\"membership_type\" type=\"hidden\" />\r\n<input id=\"amount\" name=\"amount\" type=\"hidden\" />\r\n<input id=\"period\" name=\"period\" type=\"hidden\" />\r\n<div class=\"ukroa-form-grid\"><input name=\"full_name\" required=\"\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Full Name *\" />\r\n<input name=\"email\" required=\"\" type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Email Address *\" />\r\n<input name=\"phone\" type=\"tel\" placeholder=\"Phone Number\" />\r\n<input name=\"address\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Full Address\" />\r\n<input name=\"city\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"City\" />\r\n<select name=\"country\">\r\n<option value=\"\">Select Country</option>\r\n<option value=\"USA\">USA</option>\r\n<option value=\"UK\">UK</option>\r\n<option value=\"Nepal\">Nepal</option>\r\n<option value=\"Australia\">Australia</option>\r\n<option value=\"Canada\">Canada</option>\r\n<option value=\"Other\">Other</option>\r\n</select>\r\n<input name=\"occupation\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Occupation\" />\r\n<textarea name=\"message\" rows=\"4\" placeholder=\"How did you hear about UKROA? (Optional)\"></textarea></div>\r\n<div id=\"payment-section\" style=\"margin: 30px 0;\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Payment Amount: <span id=\"pay-amount\">$30</span></strong>\r\n<div id=\"card-element\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"card-errors\" style=\"color: red; margin-top: 10px;\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<button id=\"pay-btn\" class=\"ukroa-pay-btn\" type=\"submit\">\r\n<span id=\"btn-text\">Pay &amp; Submit Application</span>\r\n<span id=\"loading\" style=\"display: none;\">Processing...</span>\r\n</button>\r\n\r\n</form></div>\r\n</div>', 'Membership', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'membership', '', '', '2025-12-06 06:41:04', '2025-12-06 11:41:04', '', 0, 'http://localhost/ukroa/?page_id=16', 0, 'page', '', 0),
